{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_550.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Bell, I finished the item you asked me for!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, really!? Lemme see, lemme see!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oooh...amazing!<CR>It turned out pretty good!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "This is perfect for my task! I wonder if Great-great-grandmother will praise me for it, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad I asked you, Ayesha! Thanks!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "You're welcome. But, what is this tool used for?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "For magic, of course. I might've told you before, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Witches use magic by extracting power from a catalyst, or by making contracts with beings of power."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "For catalysts, pure ones are more<CR>convenient, like this one that you<CR>just made me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's why we synthesize catalysts, too, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Honestly, I'm not good with those kinds of tedious things!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Haha, I see. I guess that kinda suits you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x82,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yup. My shoulders get stiff when I have to meticulously mix medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x83,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "And that's not the type of witch I'm aiming to be."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x83,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "I wanna defeat bad guys with my magic, or travel around the world, saving people!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x84,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "That's what normal witches do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I think it's more typical to see a<CR>long-nosed woman mixing mysterious<CR>potions..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Isn't that more of an alchemist thing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Maybe. I might've got them confused somewhere."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But if it was me, I could do all that meticulous work all day long without getting bored."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "You're just weird like that!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, I can finally leave my<CR>great-great-grandma speechless...<CR>I mean, get her approval!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I'm gonna take this now!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1be,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Oh, right. Thanks for today!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1c0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I'll repay you someday, physically!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Haha, I'll be looking forward to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "(I'm glad Bell was happy. But, I wonder if that was really okay...)"
        }
    ]
}